---
title: New Senior Programme Officer position at Gavi - closing date 31 December 2017
---

Gavi is [recruiting a Senior Programme Officer](http://gavialliancecareers.force.com/recruit/fRecruit__ApplyJob?vacancyNo=VN467) within its Monitoring and Evaluation team. This person will be based at the Gavi Secretariat in Geneva, and will work closely with the Vaccine Impact Modelling Consortium.     

The closing date is 31 December 2017.
